        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉勤誠各產品線出貨旺 營運逐季增 周漲逾1成重回千金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"伺服器\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:伺服器;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/伺服器\">伺服器</a>機殼廠<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"勤誠\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:勤誠;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/勤誠\">勤誠</a> (8210-TW) 受惠 AI 需求強勁，包括 AI 伺服器、通用型伺服器、存儲伺服器、交換器及機櫃零組件等產品線出貨暢旺，看好今年營運逐季增溫，激勵勤誠本周漲逾 1 成，並站回千金股行列。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勤誠本周漲 14.61%，周五 (17 日) 最高漲至 1050 元，終場收 1020 元，站回千金股。三大法人也持續敲進勤誠，連續 6 個交易日買超，合計買超 2817 張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勤誠目前除有多個 CSP 客戶新產品專案，非 CSP 客戶的 HGX 訂單亦成長。法人指出，勤誠今年在既有的 GB 及 ASIC 份額提升下，加上未來還有來自非 CSP 客戶的 HGX 訂單，看好勤誠今年營收年增雙位數。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-12603d98-25ac-31cb-b6e2-93e0e28c34f2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勤誠積極布局全球產能，美國全新 NCT(新產品導入與打樣) 廠區，已在 3 月中旬正式啟用，馬來西亞量產基地預計第三季啟用，而規模更大的美國量產廠區，則預計 2027 年完工投產。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"勤誠日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vxMc4sAfR9aXCks5hDcGvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/04a6a5a9e3b98427b6038e74c10a1afc\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">勤誠日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"勤誠各產品線需求旺 Q1淡季不淡營收年增逾7成創新高\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:勤誠各產品線需求旺 Q1淡季不淡營收年增逾7成創新高;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6412905?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">勤誠各產品線需求旺 Q1淡季不淡營收年增逾7成創新高</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"勤誠美國NCT廠區正式啟用 三大廠區接力上陣 密切關注國際四大變數\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:勤誠美國NCT廠區正式啟用 三大廠區接力上陣 密切關注國際四大變數;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnye